I"¤<p>The <code>piglow</code> platform lets you control the <a href="https://shop.pimoroni.com/products/piglow">Piglow</a> lights on your Raspberry Pi from within Home Assistant.</p>
<h2>Configuration</h2>
<p>To add piglow to your installation, add the following to your <code>configuration.yaml</code> file:</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml"># Example configuration.yaml entry
light:
  - platform: piglow
</code></pre>
